Subject: [PATCH] Brand refresh: logo, palette, footer lockup

- Standardise navy to brand #0d2c6c (was three variants: #1a2b4a, #1F3864, #1a2744)
- Standardise gold to #b8934a (was two variants: #C49A28, #b89a5a)
- Harmonise navy-mid (hover state) to #1d4291 to match new navy
- Update meta theme-color and manifest.webmanifest to #0d2c6c
- Add Aetas mark icon to .nav-logo (10 pages) and .nav-brand (8 pages)
- Add Aetas mark icon to .footer-logo (6 pages) and .footer-brand (8 pages)
- Add Aetas Partners horizontal lockup to all 24 footers, linked to aetas-partners.com
- Typography (Cormorant Garamond + Jost) unchanged
- Existing colour scheme in nav/footer logos (navy 'Aetas', gold 'in the Workplace') preserved
